Fox Shape				CATEGORY:FEAT		TYPE:General										PRERACE:1,Kitsune,RACESUBTYPE=Kitsune	PRESTAT:1,CHA=13	PRETOTALAB:3															DESC:You can change into a fox in addition to your other forms				BENEFIT:You can take the form of a fox whose appearance is static and cannot be changed each time you assume this form. Your bite attack's damage is reduced to 1d3 points of damage on a hit, but you gain a +10 racial bonus on Disguise checks made to appear as a fox. Changing from kitsune to fox shape is a standard action. This ability otherwise functions as beast shape II, and your ability scores change accordingly.
Swift Kitsune Shapechanger	CATEGORY:FEAT		TYPE:General										PRERACE:1,Kitsune,RACESUBTYPE=Kitsune				PRETOTALAB:6	PREMULT:1,[PREVARGTEQ:PreStatScore_DEX,16],[PREVARGTEQ:FeatDexRequirement,16]		DESC:You can change shape more quickly than most kitsune					BENEFIT:You can assume human or kitsune form as a swift action. If you have the Fox Shape feat, you can assume fox form as a swift action as well
Vulpine Pounce			CATEGORY:FEAT		TYPE:Combat		PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=FEAT,Swift Kitsune Shapechanger	PRERACE:1,Kitsune,RACESUBTYPE=Kitsune				PRETOTALAB:10															DESC:You can change shape mid-charge and pounce on an opponent in the same round	BENEFIT:When you change shape into your kitsune form and use the charge action in the same round, you can make a full attack against your opponent

